==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sea turtle
<hw>Sea" tur"tle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd>
<def>Any one of several very large species of chelonians having the feet
converted into paddles, as the green turtle, hawkbill, loggerhead, and
leatherback. They inhabit all warm seas.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>The sea
pigeon, or guillemot.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sea unicorn</ent>⟦br⟧
